data.description: Beautiful two story home on quiet cul-de-sac, South of Montauk in the East Islip School District. This 3000+ sqft home has an open and spacious floor plan that combines the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The living room is a showcase of contemporary design, featuring soaring ceilings, a stone wall fireplace, ceiling fans, and large picture windows that flood the room with natural light. There is an adjoining room set up as an office but can be used as a den or playroom. The large kitchen/dining area has SS appliances, granite countertops, copper farm sink and center prep and storage island with sliders leading to private side yard brick patio. The main floor also features a bedroom with a full bathroom, and a separate ensuite consisting of a bedroom area, an attached room, large walk in closet and full bath which can be used as a primary or guest ensuite-superb if you need to bring mom/dad. Main floor also has a separate powder room and laundry room. Upstairs, the grand primary suite offers a serene retreat with its own private balcony, spacious closets, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. One more bedroom and full bathroom complete the upper level. The backyard is private with brick patio and firepit for relaxing and entertaining. This home is located in a highly sought-after neighborhood and offers easy access to excellent schools, boating, parks, dining, and more. It's a perfect place to call home for those who appreciate the finer things in life. Don't miss the opportunity to make this one-of-a-kind property your own.
